    "description": "Search pharmacological interactions between targets and ligands across the Guide to Pharmacology database. Returns interaction data with affinity measurements (pKi, pIC50, pEC50), action types (agonist, antagonist, inhibitor), species, and references. Filter by target type, ligand type, affinity threshold, approved drugs, or species. Essential for finding drug-target pairs and structure-activity relationships.",
